  "name": "Deploy - Shopify Gift Vouchers",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"deploy-shopify-gift-vouchers\">Deploy - Shopify Gift Vouchers</h1>\n<p><span><span>This article explains how to deploy a Shopify Gift Vouchers licence once a signed contract has been received:</span></span></p>\n<p><span>Enable Shopify Gift Voucher Feature in MGMT</span></p>\n<p><img alt=\"rtaImage (61).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powgJEAQ.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powgJEAQ.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powgJEAQ.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powgJEAQ.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powgJEAQ.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powgJEAQ.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powgJEAQ.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powgJEAQ.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p>1. Login to <a href=\"\">MGMT</a></p>\n<p>2. Navigate to <strong>Licenses &gt; Shopify Site List</strong></p>\n<p>3. Filter by company name in <strong>Admin Link</strong></p>\n<p>4. Click on <span><strong>Edit</strong></span> and ensure that <strong>Gift Vouchers </strong>is ticked</p>\n<p>5. Select<strong> <span>Update</span></strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span>Zendesk - Sending the email </span></p>\n<p><img alt=\"gift_voucher_snip.PNG\" src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360002668776/gift_voucher_snip.PNG\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360002668776/gift_voucher_snip.PNG 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360002668776/gift_voucher_snip.PNG 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360002668776/gift_voucher_snip.PNG 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360002668776/gift_voucher_snip.PNG 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360002668776/gift_voucher_snip.PNG 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360002668776/gift_voucher_snip.PNG 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360002668776/gift_voucher_snip.PNG\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p>1. Add a new ticket</p>\n<p>2. Add the email address for the contact on the solutions agreement</p>\n<p>3. Select the macro <strong>Implementation &gt; Shopify Gift Vouchers: Getting Started</strong></p>\n<p>5. Submit the ticket as Solved</p>",
